           CALL WS-PGMID
                USING VIAL4000-COMMAREA
              ON EXCEPTION
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-ARQ   TO VIAL4000-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-TRN-NOTFND  TO VIAL4000-NRERRO
                MOVE WS-PGMID             TO VIAL4000-PGMID
           END-CALL.
